OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FVenice to ban large tourist
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgroups and loudspeakers    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Venice is to ban loudspeakers and      
OL,6, tourist groups of more than 25 people, 
OL,7, in a bid to ease the impact of mass    
OL,8, tourism on the Italian city.           
OL,10,FThe new rules will come into effect    
OL,11,Ffrom June, the city said in a          
OL,12,Fstatement.                             
OL,14,FThe use of loudspeakers have been      
OL,15,Fbanned as they can "generate confusion 
OL,16,Fand disturbances", it added.           
OL,18,FOver-tourism is widely recognised as an
OL,19,Furgent issue for the canal city, one of
OL,20,Fthe most visited places in Europe.     
